<% content_for :page_title, "Landing Page" %>
<div class="app-masthead">
  <div class="govuk-width-container">
    <%= render "shared/phase_banner" %>

    <div class="govuk-grid-row">
      <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
        <h1 class="govuk-heading-xl govuk-!-margin-top-4 govuk-!-margin-bottom-6">
          Search for cosmetic products
        </h1>
        <p class="masthead-account-links govuk-!-padding-top-2 govuk-!-margin-bottom-5">
          <%= govukButton text: "Sign in", href: keycloak_login_url(dashboard_path) %>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-width-container">
  <main id="main-content" class="govuk-main-wrapper app-main-class" role="main">
    <div class="govuk-grid-row">
      <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
        <p class="govuk-body-lead">Search for cosmetic products available in the UK and notified with the Office for Product Safety and Standards (OPSS).</p>

        <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">How to access the service</h2>

        <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-bottom-2">If you’re using this service for the first time, send an email to <a href="mailto:opss.enquiries@beis.gov.uk">opss.enquiries@beis.gov.uk</a> to ask for an account.</p>

        <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Trading Standards officers</h3>

        <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-bottom-2">If you’ve used the Product Safety Database (PSD), you can use your PSD sign in details (username and password).</p>

        <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">What you can search for</h2>

        <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-bottom-2">You can search for cosmetic products by:</p>

        <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
          <li>product name</li>
          <li>product category</li>
          <li>responsible person</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="govuk-inset-text">The ‘responsible person’ (RP) is the company (or individual) responsible for ensuring the regulations are followed. Every cosmetic product placed on the UK market must have an RP.</div>

        <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">National Poison Information Service (NPIS) staff</h3>

        <p class="govuk-body">You can find out the ingredients in a cosmetics product.</p>

        <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Trading Standards officers</h3>

        <p class="govuk-body">You can check if the cosmetic product has been notified with OPSS.</p>

        <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">What you can't search for</h2>

        <p class="govuk-body">You can't search for cosmetic products taken off the UK market before 1 February 2020 but still used in the UK.</p>

        <div class="govuk-inset-text">Some ingredient information and packaging images may be missing for cosmetic products notified with the EU before 1 February 2020.</div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</div>
